-- Estacio Raised to `Buy' From `Hold' at Santander on `Attractive Valuation'
-- Shiyin Chen
-- 2010-06-21T02:37:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/estacio-raised-to-buy-from-hold-at-santander-on-attractive-valuation-.html

          
          
             Estacio Participacoes SA was raised
to “buy” from “hold” by Banco Santander SA analysts Daniel
Gewehr and Bruno Giardino, who said the shares have reached an
“attractive valuation level” after their declines this year.  
